{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are Ka-Hool, a ghost, that remembers nothing but their name. Awaken in a cave, your goal is to look for your past, to look for your identity. Throughout this adventure, you\u2019ll rediscover your own abilities, stroll through the remains of an ancient world, and continue your journey for memory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_en_world.png?t=1734691482\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_lostworld_30fps.gif?t=1734691482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remains of a mysterious civilisation lay ahead. Who were they? How did they disappear? Your quest for memory will cross a quest for history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_en_possess.png?t=1734691482\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_possess2_30fsp.gif?t=1734691482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ka-Hool is nothing of an ordinary ghost: take control of the beasts that creep in the shadows to progress in your adventure. Each creature has unique abilities, use them wisely! Yet beware, the depths have their own ecosystem, and not all creatures can be fooled.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_en_past.png?t=1734691482\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_past_30fps.gif?t=1734691482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travelling through the world will take you to different sublime sceneries, and your quest for knowledge will be shaped by challenges and fragments of the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_en_light.png?t=1734691482\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_creatures2_30fps.gif?t=1734691482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This world is beautiful but filled with radiant dangers. In your spectral form, the light is your greatest foe, and you must avoid it at all costs. Choose your path wisely, or risk a shining demise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2108640/extras/afs_en_social.png?t=1734691482\" /> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Expert Swimmer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2108640/208749e089ac824bc90b74b3dd55c7500bcf838b.jpg"},{"name":"Nosy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2108640/c1737c8f2f896a838f0aa11d6503feb1677ae892.jpg"},{"name":"Free as a Bird","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2108640/efdc1d802b075cbda7377ec76742c89480dc65b5.jpg"},{"name":"Invisible","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2108640/bbd41c8e12c07b0eab1d4a170450531145b89bfe.jpg"},{"name":"Illumination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2108640/19484f051dbbebc5c1f6e6a4aaa7f6fbe3088b1d.jpg"},{"name":"Strange energy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2108640/42edcf08f8fefc64209e0045d2382af6e65aff1c.jpg"},{"name":"No more Secrets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2108640/c81652b8ae8688c41d30e093faf0bf394d0